@VirtualLibrary.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5179

### Health
GET {{VirtualLibrary.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Admin login
POST {{VirtualLibrary.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@virtuallibrary.local",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Lookup an ISBN
POST {{VirtualLibrary.Api_HostAddress}}/api/lookup/9780140328721
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
